        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *lesser reinforced wooden shield* (Hardness 6, HP 64, BT 32) is painted with intricate, pale-blue knots. The wood has been magically enhanced against solar energy and heat. While you have this shield raised, you gain fire resistance 5.",
